            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052374/Polytechnisch woordenboek En-Ne (1991)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>磚石牆內嵌有不透水材料的水平層，用來防止水分向上之毛細管運動或其向下滲漏。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
